title: Randy Jackson's China Rain - Bed Of Nails (FLAC)
description:
Beyond Records release of Bed Of Nails by China Rain. With Randy Jackson of Zebra, 

and guest appearances from Dave "Snake" Sabo (Skid Row) and Mark Slaughter 

(Slaughter, Vinnie Vincent Invasion). Ripped to FLAC Lossless Audio.


Track Listing:
1. You're Only Lonely Today
2. Bang On The Wall
3. Psychedelic Sex Reaction
4. Last Forever
5. Light Of My Love
6. Bed Of Nails
7. Before It's Too Late
8. I Loved You Lied
9. Valerine
10. Love Calls

Released in 1991
